
# tap repositories and their packages

## caskroom/cask
tap caskroom/cask
install brew-cask
cask install dropbox
cask install google-chrome
cask install google-japanese-ime
cask install iterm2

## rcmdnk/file
tap rcmdnk/file
install brew-file

# Other Homebrew packages
install git

